skdetail:

Invocation Name: interview simulator
des: iPG is a basic Y-Combinator interview simulator which asks general questions about you and your company, akin to the questions in which you may be asked in a real Y-Combinator, or any incubator/investor, interview. Adapted from the iPG web app written by James Cunningham and Colin Hayhurst (https://github.com/jamescun/iPG).
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
